@startuml 02-sequence-delete-route
title deleteRoute hard delete (row first, Storage second)

actor Yuki
participant "Browser\n(RouteList +\nDeleteRouteButton)" as Browser
participant "Radix AlertDialog" as Dialog
participant "deleteRoute\n(Server Action · Node)" as Action
participant "Postgres\nroutes (RLS)" as DB
participant "Supabase Storage\n(gpx bucket · RLS)" as Storage
participant "Next.js cache\nrevalidatePath()" as Cache

Yuki -> Browser : 在 /admin/routes 列表按某 row「刪除」
Browser -> Dialog : open AlertDialog\n「將永久刪除 {title}（含 GPX 原檔）」

alt 取消
  Yuki -> Dialog : 按「取消」
  Dialog --> Browser : close
end

Yuki -> Dialog : 按「確認刪除」
Dialog -> Action : deleteRoute({ id })

Action -> DB : ① SELECT gpx_path FROM routes WHERE id=$1
alt 0 rows (id 已不存在)
  DB --> Action : []
  Action --> Browser : { ok:true }   ' idempotent
  note right of Action
    這條 flow 在 race 下保護
    Yuki 從別瀏覽器同步刪了
  end note
end
DB --> Action : { gpx_path }

Action -> DB : ② DELETE FROM routes WHERE id=$1\n[RLS: admin_full_access]
alt DB DELETE throw
  DB --> Action : throw
  Action --> Browser : { ok:false, message:'刪除失敗' }
end
DB --> Action : ok

note over Action, Storage
  row 已刪 → gpx_public_select_published
  policy 的 EXISTS 條件失效，
  剩下 Storage object 對 anon 已不可讀
end note

Action -> Storage : ③ storage.from('gpx').remove([gpx_path])\n[RLS: gpx_admin_delete]
alt Storage remove throw (best-effort)
  Storage --> Action : throw
  Action -> Action : console.warn('orphan gpx file', path, e)
  Action --> Browser : { ok:true }   ' row 已刪，orphan 不影響可見性
end
Storage --> Action : ok

Action -> Cache : ④ revalidatePath('/routes')\nrevalidatePath('/routes/'+slug)\nrevalidatePath('/admin/routes')
Action --> Browser : { ok:true }

Browser -> Browser : router.refresh()\nsonner toast「已刪除 ${title}」
Browser --> Yuki : 列表少一條 + toast

@enduml
